jects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection","title":"MLNPointCollection","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPointCollection"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"disconnected vertices, specified as "},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instances. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"orchard."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","title":"MLNPolyline","identifier":"do